name: Giovanni Battista Crivellari
personality: Giovanni is young and ambitious, eager to implement new techniques in window making and prove his abilities to the influential guild elders.

name: Francesco Buccio
personality: Francesco is eager to bring new ideas to his trade, keen to demonstrate his dedication and creativity to the established guild members.

name: Gaetano Verocai
personality: Gaetano is a proud artisan, struggling to make ends meet but insists on honest dealings to maintain his dignity.

name: Andrea Molinari
personality: Andrea is a passionate woodworker who finds immense joy in crafting beautiful and intricate designs, valuing the artistry over monetary gain. He often reflects on the philosophy of craftsmanship, believing that his work connects him to both his ancestors and future generations.

name: Iseppo MInio
personality: Iseppo Minio is a reserved and introverted tailor, dedicated to his craft and family, seldom seen at social gatherings.

name: Illustrissimo Signor Francesco quondam Iseppo BIanchi
personality: Francesco is an ambitious wood merchant who dreams of rising in status, often engaging with influential figures and participating in prestigious confraternities.

name: Gasparo de Gaspari
personality: Gasparo is a nostalgic soul, often reminiscing about the bustling days of his youth when his shop was the talk of the town. He remains resistant to modern innovations in pastry making, preferring to stick to traditional recipes passed down through generations.

name: Nicolò Panciera
personality: Nicolò is aging and nostalgic, often reminiscing about the vibrant past of his trade while resisting modern innovations.

name: Antonio Costantini
personality: Antonio is a traditional and conservative fruit vendor who adheres strictly to the time-honored practices of his guild, and regards change and newcomers with suspicion.

name: Mattio Mucitelli
personality: Mattio is an artistic craftsman who takes great pleasure in the presentation and quality of his vegetables, often reflecting philosophically on the connection between nature and sustenance.

name: Francesco Martignoni
personality: Francesco is a laid-back individual who values leisure time over profit, often indulging in wine and idling about his shop.

name: Girolamo Degan
personality: Girolamo is jovial and social, knowing everyone in his neighborhood. He loves to engage in gossip, often prioritizing social interactions over his business.

name: Antonio Marchetti
personality: Antonio is meticulous about the quality of his produce, often spending extra time arranging them artistically. He finds joy in conversations with his customers, discussing not only vegetables but life's poetry.

name: Antonio Formenti
personality: Antonio is a reserved and introverted shoemaker who keeps to himself, focusing solely on his family and work. He avoids social gatherings and prefers the quiet life in his small shop.

name: Francesco Gambaroto
personality: Francesco is reserved and introverted, often keeping to himself and focusing primarily on his family. He avoids social gatherings and prefers the solitude and routine of his work.

name: Giambattista Galvan
personality: Giambattista is deeply pious and sees his business as a service to God. He is close with the local clergy and attends mass daily, believing that his success is a blessing to be shared with the community.

name: Alvise Tagliaferro
personality: Alvise seeks to elevate his status by associating with the wealthy and influential. He takes pride in his shop and often acts condescendingly towards those in lesser trades.

name: Nicolò Fossati
personality: Nicolò is a sentimental man, often reminiscing about his youth when the paper trade was more lucrative. He prefers the traditional methods and is averse to adopting modern practices.

name: Pietro Bertoli
personality: Although deeply connected to his craft in Venice, Pietro often reminisces fondly about his visits to the mainland where he sources exquisite silks and feels a sense of belonging.

name: Daniel Moro
personality: Daniel Moro is status-seeking, aspiring to rise above his current station by associating with prestigious confraternities and showing disdain for common trades.

name: Alessandro Licini
personality: Young and ambitious, Alessandro is eager to innovate and prove his worth to the guild elders by introducing new sales tactics and forming strong connections with local suppliers.

name: Iseppo Orio
personality: Shrewd and calculating - always thinking about profit, expands business aggressively, not particularly religious.

name: Marco Tagliaferro
personality: Marco Tagliaferro is a wealthy and generous merchant who is known for his prosperous business in second-hand fabrics. He is dedicated to supporting the poor and contributes generously to church festivals.

name: Pietro Franchin
personality: Pietro is a status-seeking individual who aspires to mingle with the Venetian nobility by perfecting his craft in jewellery making and attending prestigious confraternities.

name: Pietro Giacomazzi
personality: Pietro Giacomazzi is shrewd and calculating, always thinking about profit and expanding his business aggressively. He is not particularly religious, focusing instead on the practicalities of life.

name: Ferigo Genico Scaletter quondam Lazaro
personality: Ferigo is skeptical and practical, dismissing superstition and focusing on efficiency. He respects only tangible results in his craft and dealings.

name: Giacomo Succhietti
personality: Giacomo is reserved and introverted, focusing solely on his family's well-being rather than engaging in social activities.

name: Francesco Maestrini
personality: Francesco is skeptical and practical, dismissing superstition with a focus on efficiency and respecting only tangible results.

name: Bortolo Sanzonio
personality: Bortolo Sanzonio takes pride in crafting the finest pasta, even as he struggles to make a profit; his integrity in business is unwavering.

name: Anzolo Redolfi
personality: Anzolo Redolfi is a traditional and conservative jeweller who meticulously follows the old guild ways, showing a cautious distrust towards change and newcomers.

name: Zuanne del Favro
personality: Zuanne is deeply pious, attending mass daily and maintaining a close relationship with the local clergy, viewing his craftsmanship as a form of service to God.

name: Bastian Pagiaro
personality: Bastian Pagiaro is skeptical and practical, dismissing superstition and focusing on efficiency. He respects only results and values hard work.

name: Antonio Pizzioli
personality: Antonio is a jovial and social man who knows everyone in his neighborhood. He loves gossip and often spends his evenings at local taverns, considering his business as secondary to his social interactions.

name: Zuanne Battista Carminati
personality: Zuanne is carefree and lazy, often seen enjoying a glass of wine rather than focusing on his metalwork. Despite his lackadaisical approach, he manages to keep his business just above water.

name: Andrea Ruggieri
personality: Andrea Ruggieri is ambitious and constantly seeks ways to elevate his social standing. He is a member of several elite confraternities and often disdains fellow tradesmen who lack his aspirations.

name: Giulian Semenzato
personality: Giulian is a struggling but proud fruit seller who barely makes ends meet yet maintains his dignity through honest dealing.

name: Giulio de Bara
personality: Giulio is a hard-working and honest shoemaker, barely making ends meet yet maintaining his dignity through fair and honest dealings.

name: Bortolo Borali
personality: Bortolo Borali is deeply pious and devout, attending mass daily and maintaining close ties with the local clergy. He sees his business as a service to God and treats every interaction as a testament to his faith.

name: Giulio Botti
personality: Giulio is a status-seeking individual who takes pride in his luxurious jewellery shop, aspiring to mingle with the nobility. He is a member of prestigious confraternities and often looks down on common trades.

name: Antonio Plateo
personality: Antonio is deeply pious and devout, attending mass daily and maintaining close relationships with the clergy. He sees his chair-making business as a service to God, ensuring quality in every piece as a testament to his faith.

name: Pietro Filosi
personality: Pietro is young and ambitious, recently established in his trade, eager to innovate and prove his worth to the guild elders by introducing new wine blends.

name: Orsetta Maggia vedova
personality: Orsetta is carefree and lazy, enjoying her time with a glass of wine more than running her shop, yet somehow she manages to keep her business going.

name: Zuanne Zanchi
personality: Zuanne Zanchi is deeply pious and devout, attending mass daily and maintaining a close relationship with the clergy. He sees his business dealings as a service to God, providing necessary medicines and spices to the community.

name: Zuanne Fornaser
personality: Zuanne is aging and nostalgic, often reminiscing about his earlier days when his fruit stall was bustling with activity. He is resistant to adopting new methods, preferring the traditional ways he's known all his life.

name: Gasparo Gobbis
personality: Young and ambitious, Gasparo is recently established, eager to innovate and prove his worth to the guild elders.

name: Giacomo Gozzi
personality: Giacomo Gozzi is a jovial and social man, known for his friendly demeanor and love of gossip. He enjoys spending his evenings at local taverns, treating business as a secondary affair to socializing.

name: Piero Pellegrini
personality: Piero Pellegrini is a wealthy and generous man, known for running a prosperous water selling business. He is well-regarded in the community for his charitable contributions and support of local church festivals.

name: Francesco Astori
personality: Francesco Astori is young and ambitious, having recently established his shop. He is eager to innovate and prove his worth to the guild elders.

name: Pietro Lissignolo
personality: Pietro is struggling but proud, barely making ends meet in his sausage shop, yet he maintains dignity through honest dealing.

name: Francesco Fornaser
personality: Francesco is wealthy and generous, running a prosperous fruit business. He is known for supporting the poor and funding church festivals.
